name: Blade Bunny
description: In the forest south of the kingdom's capital the influence of the Litch created these brutal, deadly and extremely cute monsters."the Tome of monsters and beasts" describes the Blade Bunnies as very cunning creatures, it also says that they usually hunt in packs using stratagems in fact there are documented episodes of adventurers who approached by one of them who hid the tail made of muscles and tendons, were then attacked by the entire pack.
